<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 06:21:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于中国需求减弱，飞利浦下调销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/philips-lowers-sales-outlook-china-demand-wanes-2024-10-28/</link><description>荷兰医疗设备制造商飞利浦周一下调了今年的销售预期，原因是中国需求下降，导致其第三季度订单量下降了 2%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 06:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/philips-lowers-sales-outlook-china-demand-wanes-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国再次警告欧盟不要与电动汽车制造商单独谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-again-warns-eu-against-separate-talks-with-ev-makers-2024-10-28/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，中国再次向欧盟发出警告，如果欧盟在与中国谈判的同时与电动汽车公司单独进行谈判，将“动摇互信”并干扰整体谈判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 06:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-again-warns-eu-against-separate-talks-with-ev-makers-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>一些公司在中国改变策略，看不到复苏的迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/some-companies-change-tack-china-with-no-recovery-sight-2024-10-28/</link><description>由于房地产危机和失业率上升，客户正在削减支出。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 05:06:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/some-companies-change-tack-china-with-no-recovery-sight-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>上海警方出动警力制止喧闹的万圣节庆祝活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/police-out-force-prevent-rowdy-halloween-celebrations-shanghai-2024-10-28/</link><description>周末，上海警方在市中心街道巡逻，打击这座中国最国际化城市的万圣节庆祝活动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 03:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/police-out-force-prevent-rowdy-halloween-celebrations-shanghai-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国的私人辅导公司在镇压后走出阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-private-tutoring-firms-emerge-shadows-after-crackdown-2024-10-28/</link><description>目前还没有正式承认政策的变化。但现在政策制定者已经默许辅导行业的发展，北京方面的重点是支持创造就业机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 02:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-private-tutoring-firms-emerge-shadows-after-crackdown-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中东喘息而下滑，日元因日本政府失去多数席位而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-28/</link><description>由于日本执政党失去了议会多数席位，日元周一触及三个月低点，而以色列周末对伊朗的袭击绕过了石油或核目标后，油价暴跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 00:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国在年底贷款到期前推出新的贷款工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-activates-open-market-outright-reverse-repo-operations-2024-10-28/</link><description>中国央行周一推出了新的贷款工具，以在年底数万亿人民币贷款到期之前向市场注入更多流动性，并支持银行体系的信贷流动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 00:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-activates-open-market-outright-reverse-repo-operations-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，中国黑客从未透露姓名的特朗普竞选顾问那里收集了音频</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/chinese-hackers-collected-audio-unnamed-trump-campaign-adviser-washington-post-2024-10-27/</link><description>据《华盛顿邮报》周日报道，中国政府相关黑客截获了美国政治人物的电话音频，其中包括共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的一位未透露姓名的竞选顾问。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/chinese-hackers-collected-audio-unnamed-trump-campaign-adviser-washington-post-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>北京猛烈抨击美国军火交易后，台湾报告中国“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</link><description>美国批准了一项可能为台湾提供的价值 20 亿美元的一揽子计划，其中包括向台湾提供在乌克兰经过实战考验的先进防空导弹系统。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 00:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国领导的亚投行行长批评发达国家贸易壁垒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-led-aiib-head-criticizes-advanced-nations-trade-barriers-2024-10-26/</link><description>亚洲基础设施投资银行（亚投行）行长金立群周六批评发达经济体设置贸易壁垒，包括可再生能源产品，称全球经济“不再自由贸易”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 15:36:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-led-aiib-head-criticizes-advanced-nations-trade-barriers-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，在华为处理器上发现芯片后，台积电暂停向中国公司发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-suspended-shipments-china-firm-after-chip-found-huawei-processor-sources-2024-10-26/</link><description>华为被限制购买该技术以保护美国国家安全。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 15:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-suspended-shipments-china-firm-after-chip-found-huawei-processor-sources-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国在美国会议上表达对关税和制裁的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-expresses-concern-over-tariffs-sanctions-us-meeting-2024-10-26/</link><description>中国财政部周六表示，中国在华盛顿举行的两国经济工作组会议上表达了对美国关税和与俄罗斯相关制裁的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 08:16:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-expresses-concern-over-tariffs-sanctions-us-meeting-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国批准向台湾出售价值20亿美元的武器，其中包括乌克兰测试的导弹系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-potential-2-billion-arms-sale-taiwan-week-after-chinese-war-games-2024-10-26/</link><description>中国不断加大对台湾的军事压力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 02:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-potential-2-billion-arms-sale-taiwan-week-after-chinese-war-games-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国黑客针对与哈里斯竞选活动有关的手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-targeted-phones-used-by-trump-vance-new-york-times-reports-2024-10-25/</link><description>一位知情人士周五表示，侵入 Verizon 系统的中国黑客瞄准了与民主党总统候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 竞选活动有关联的人员使用的手机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-targeted-phones-used-by-trump-vance-new-york-times-reports-2024-10-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大电动汽车部门停止讨论股权出售事宜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-ev-unit-cease-discussions-stake-sale-2024-10-25/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周五表示，其潜在卖家已决定停止出售该公司股权的谈判，该公司是负债累累的中国恒大的电动汽车部门。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 14:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-ev-unit-cease-discussions-stake-sale-2024-10-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>